last_episode_to_air.name: Sleepover
last_episode_to_air.overview: Beavis and Butt-Head are invited to sleep over at Cody's house when his parents mistakenly think they're good friends.

name: Mike Judge's Beavis and Butt-Head
overview: Two teenage heavy-metal music fans occasionally do idiotic things because they're bored. For them, everything is "cool" or "sucks."
tagline: All new reasons to stay on the couch.

episodes.name: Escape Room
episodes.overview: Beavis and Butt-Head try to solve an Escape Room only to wind up trapped in the bathroom.

episodes.name: The Special One
episodes.overview: Beavis meets his greatest hero, Fire.

episodes.name: Boxed In
episodes.overview: Beavis and Butt-Head get trapped in a cardboard box while attempting to hide out in the school.

episodes.name: Beekeepers
episodes.overview: Beavis and Butt-Head try to harvest honey from a wasps' nest.

episodes.name: Roof

episodes.name: River

episodes.name: Two Stupid Men
episodes.overview: Middle-aged Beavis and Butt-Head fulfill their civic duty as jurors.

episodes.name: Freaky Friday

episodes.name: Weird Girl
episodes.overview: Beavis encounters a secret admirer at school.

episodes.name: Time Travelers
episodes.overview: Beavis and Butt-Head cross back and forth across the state line into the Mountain Time Zone and think they can travel through time.

episodes.name: Spiritual Journey
episodes.overview: Beavis sees the face of Jesus in a nacho chip, setting him on an epic journey to seek answers to the big question - "Why do I never score?"

episodes.name: Refuse Service
episodes.overview: The boys discover they have the right to refuse service to customers at Burger World.

episodes.name: Downward Dumbass
episodes.overview: Beavis tries on yoga pants and can't get them off.

episodes.name: The Most Dangerous Game
episodes.overview: In order to prevent the other from putting their hand in a bowl of warm water, causing them to pee their pants, Beavis and Butt-Head stay awake for several days.

episodes.name: Bone Hunters
episodes.overview: Beavis and Butt-Head construct a dinosaur skeleton out of bones from a BBQ.

episodes.name: Meditation Sucks
episodes.overview: Beavis and Butt-Head try to empty their minds and find they are surprisingly good at it.

episodes.name: Polling Place

episodes.name: Old Man Beavis
episodes.overview: Butt-Head makes Beavis look old so he can buy beer. Beavis ends up in a senior living facility and almost scores with an 80-year-old woman.

episodes.name: Hunting Trip
episodes.overview: Tom Anderson takes Beavis and Butt-Head to the woods to hunt deer.

episodes.name: Pardon Our Dust
episodes.overview: Middle-aged Beavis and Butt-Head attend a city council meeting to get their apartment demolished.

episodes.name: Pranks

episodes.name: Hellhole
episodes.overview: Beavis and Butt-Head fall into a sewer and think they have died and gone to hell.

episodes.name: Take a Bow

episodes.name: Tobacco Farmers
episodes.overview: Beavis and Butt-Head try to grow their own tobacco like George Washington.

episodes.name: Married

episodes.name: Sad Boys
episodes.overview: After they see the attention an angsty emo kid gets from the ladies, Beavis and Butt-Head pretend to be sad and end up in a psychiatric hospital.

episodes.name: Are You There God? It's Me, Beavis.
episodes.overview: Beavis notices his body is starting to go through changes after he is bitten by a rabid raccoon.

episodes.name: The Day Butt-Head Went Too Far
episodes.overview: Beavis decides he has finally had enough and hires a hitman to kill Butt-Head.

episodes.name: Spring Break

episodes.overview: Beavis and Butt-Head try to get rich by breeding dogs with a raccoon they found in a garbage can.

episodes.name: Hoarders
episodes.overview: Beavis and Butt-Head fill their house with garbage to meet girls.

episodes.name: Needle Dicks
episodes.overview: Beavis and Butt-Head try acupuncture, and Beavis decides to spend the rest of his life with 50 needles in his face.

episodes.name: The Ciabatta Zone
episodes.overview: Beavis and Butt-Head both want to wear the Burger World giant hamburger costume.

episodes.name: Warehouse
episodes.overview: Middle-aged Beavis and Butt-Head get a warehouse job at the world's biggest internet retail company. You know the one we mean.

episodes.name: Abduction
episodes.overview: Smart Beavis and Smart Butt-Head visit Earth and abduct Tom Anderson for human experiments.
